feature?

00:01:00.049 --> 00:01:02.280
Leave me a comment and let me know!

00:01:02.280 --> 00:01:05.110
And you can check the full announcement on
the Steam Store page if you want to read more

00:01:05.110 --> 00:01:06.960
about how Family Sharing will work.

